Use websocket king for websocket connection
socket url : ws://localhost:8080/socket

subsribe request data :

{
  "action": "subscribe",
  "topic": "world"
}

unsubsribe request data:
{
  "action": "unsubscribe",
  "topic": "world"
}

rest url :http://localhost:8080/publish
method post
publish request body 
{
  "topic":"world",
  "message":"something"
}